WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:08.466 align:middle line:90%


00:00:08.466 --> 00:00:12.460 align:middle line:90%
[MUSIC PLAYING]

00:00:12.460 --> 00:00:43.728 align:middle line:90%


00:00:43.728 --> 00:00:46.680 align:middle line:84%
Well, when I was a young child,
like, four or five years old,

00:00:46.680 --> 00:00:49.990 align:middle line:84%
I remember very
clearly reading a book,

00:00:49.990 --> 00:00:53.200 align:middle line:84%
and it was called, The
Boy Who Sang to the World.

00:00:53.200 --> 00:00:57.020 align:middle line:84%
In this book, a boy
would sing to the world,

00:00:57.020 --> 00:00:58.600 align:middle line:84%
and he would sing
their dreams come true.

00:00:58.600 --> 00:01:09.820 align:middle line:90%


00:01:09.820 --> 00:01:12.910 align:middle line:84%
I lost the book, and
then I started searching,

00:01:12.910 --> 00:01:15.190 align:middle line:90%
and there no such book exists.

00:01:15.190 --> 00:01:18.400 align:middle line:84%
I was reading it in some
other realm of consciousness.

00:01:18.400 --> 00:01:21.300 align:middle line:84%
And for me, that's
what I became,

00:01:21.300 --> 00:01:23.220 align:middle line:84%
was the boy who
sang to the world.

00:01:23.220 --> 00:01:25.860 align:middle line:90%


00:01:25.860 --> 00:01:28.630 align:middle line:90%
[MUSIC PLAYING]

00:01:28.630 --> 00:02:14.190 align:middle line:90%


00:02:14.190 --> 00:02:19.250 align:middle line:84%
I think that the entire human
collective is in a dark night

00:02:19.250 --> 00:02:20.180 align:middle line:90%
of the soul right now.

00:02:20.180 --> 00:02:27.515 align:middle line:90%


00:02:27.515 --> 00:02:31.290 align:middle line:84%
The despair and the
hopelessness of humanity

00:02:31.290 --> 00:02:37.180 align:middle line:84%
is just breathtaking
and beyond words,

00:02:37.180 --> 00:02:41.420 align:middle line:84%
and the ecosystem is screaming,
and no one knows what to do.

00:02:41.420 --> 00:02:48.510 align:middle line:90%


00:02:48.510 --> 00:02:53.390 align:middle line:84%
My only hope is you hit that
dark point of no return,

00:02:53.390 --> 00:02:57.490 align:middle line:84%
and you are in it for a while,
and then something turns.

00:02:57.490 --> 00:03:02.390 align:middle line:10%
And new ideas will bubble up,
new solutions will come forward

00:03:02.390 --> 00:03:06.832 align:middle line:10%
for us to change the
course of our history,

00:03:06.832 --> 00:03:09.090 align:middle line:10%
and we'll come out of the
depths of the human heart

00:03:09.090 --> 00:03:12.296 align:middle line:10%
and mind in a way that
we can't anticipate.

00:03:12.296 --> 00:03:16.264 align:middle line:90%
[MUSIC PLAYING]

00:03:16.264 --> 00:03:19.036 align:middle line:90%


00:03:19.036 --> 00:03:23.392 align:middle line:90%
[CHANTING AND SINGING]

00:03:23.392 --> 00:04:21.140 align:middle line:90%


00:04:21.140 --> 00:04:23.780 align:middle line:84%
The ancient traditions,
they all speak to it.

00:04:23.780 --> 00:04:27.190 align:middle line:84%
The mystery in Genesis-- in
the beginning was the word,

00:04:27.190 --> 00:04:29.380 align:middle line:84%
and the word said,
let there be light.

00:04:29.380 --> 00:04:34.548 align:middle line:84%
So before light, there was sound
vibration, or vibration itself.

00:04:34.548 --> 00:04:38.090 align:middle line:84%
And in the Vedic traditions
of ancient India,

00:04:38.090 --> 00:04:41.950 align:middle line:84%
Brahma uttered
the sound ohm, and

00:04:41.950 --> 00:04:43.724 align:middle line:90%
everything came into existence.

00:04:43.724 --> 00:04:46.688 align:middle line:90%
[CHANTING AND SINGING]

00:04:46.688 --> 00:04:50.150 align:middle line:90%


00:04:50.150 --> 00:04:52.580 align:middle line:84%
The first movement
of a particle,

00:04:52.580 --> 00:04:55.820 align:middle line:84%
when it starts to vibrate,
it creates a frequency,

00:04:55.820 --> 00:04:58.480 align:middle line:90%
and it's a sound or a vibration.

00:04:58.480 --> 00:05:00.520 align:middle line:84%
From the smallest
subatomic particle

00:05:00.520 --> 00:05:03.000 align:middle line:84%
to the largest galaxies--
including our bodies--

00:05:03.000 --> 00:05:04.190 align:middle line:90%
it began with sound.

