01:02:53.050 --> 01:02:58.800 align:middle line:84%
He had a golden aura, and
he is very, very ancient,

01:02:58.800 --> 01:03:03.100 align:middle line:84%
and he has seen many human
civilizations come and go.

01:03:03.100 --> 01:03:06.310 align:middle line:84%
And he was deeply
saddened and dismayed

01:03:06.310 --> 01:03:11.040 align:middle line:84%
by how humans treat the Earth
and the beings of the Earth.

01:03:11.040 --> 01:03:15.920 align:middle line:84%
And his message is that human
beings must honor the Earth,

01:03:15.920 --> 01:03:17.134 align:middle line:90%
or they will not survive.

01:03:17.134 --> 01:03:29.010 align:middle line:90%


01:03:29.010 --> 01:03:31.440 align:middle line:84%
Early on, I started
having impressions

01:03:31.440 --> 01:03:36.195 align:middle line:84%
of mountains, and the
Himalayas, and what

01:03:36.195 --> 01:03:37.490 align:middle line:90%
I later recognized to be Tibet.

01:03:37.490 --> 01:03:41.670 align:middle line:90%


01:03:41.670 --> 01:03:44.380 align:middle line:84%
And what I experienced in
a very primal, direct way,

01:03:44.380 --> 01:03:49.820 align:middle line:84%
was that I was deeply connected
to Tibet, and to Padmasambhava,

01:03:49.820 --> 01:03:52.010 align:middle line:84%
who had brought Buddhism into
Tibet in the 7th century,

01:03:52.010 --> 01:03:57.480 align:middle line:84%
and also to Yeshe Tsogyal, who
was his tantric practitioner

01:03:57.480 --> 01:03:59.450 align:middle line:90%
that joined him.

01:03:59.450 --> 01:04:14.720 align:middle line:90%
[SINGING AND CHANTING]

01:04:14.720 --> 01:04:16.494 align:middle line:90%


01:04:16.494 --> 01:04:17.660 align:middle line:84%
[CHANTING IN NON ENGLISH
 LANGUAGE]

01:04:17.660 --> 01:04:23.060 align:middle line:90%


01:04:23.060 --> 01:04:24.940 align:middle line:84%
I was already
initiated into Buddhism,

01:04:24.940 --> 01:04:32.390 align:middle line:84%
