 OVERTURE"]

01:14:40.822 --> 01:14:42.148 align:middle line:90%
And the calvary's heading in.

01:14:42.148 --> 01:14:44.760 align:middle line:84%
It's a race, and
they've almost got it.

01:14:44.760 --> 01:14:45.890 align:middle line:90%
The first one there wins.

01:14:45.890 --> 01:14:46.890 align:middle line:90%
Yay, yay, yay!

01:14:46.890 --> 01:14:49.265 align:middle line:90%
