I'm not going to take
you or you or you.

01:15:01.661 --> 01:15:04.420 align:middle line:84%
Not you.
And, god, definitely not you.

01:15:04.420 --> 01:15:06.110 align:middle line:90%
Ah, yes, you.

01:15:06.110 --> 01:15:08.510 align:middle line:90%
Come on over.

01:15:08.510 --> 01:15:11.120 align:middle line:84%
And she opens the molecular
door just big enough

01:15:11.120 --> 01:15:12.360 align:middle line:90%
