01:15:19.970 --> 01:15:22.490 align:middle line:84%
And from that moment, mitosis
begins, and [ZOOMING SOUND]

01:15:22.490 --> 01:15:24.590 align:middle line:90%
here we are.

01:15:24.590 --> 01:15:28.320 align:middle line:84%
So the wisdom of the
egg doesn't just take

01:15:28.320 --> 01:15:29.600 align:middle line:90%
the first comer, so to speak.

01:15:29.600 --> 01:15:32.710 align:middle line:90%


01:15:32.710 --> 01:15:33.545 align:middle line:90%
I didn't plan that pun.

01:15:33.545 --> 01:15:37.690 align:middle line:84%
It honestly just happened,
but-- when you find treasures,

01:15:37.690 --> 01:15:40.850 align:middle line:84%
you must pick them up, unless
there are strings attached.

01:15:40.850 --> 01:15:44.130 align:middle line:90%


01:15:44.130 --> 01:15:46.920 align:middle line:84%
So you got here as an expression
of feminine intelligence.

01:15:46.920 --> 01:15:54.240 align:middle line:90%


01:15:54.240 --> 01:15:58.160 align:middle line:90%
[SOUND OF STORM]

01:15:58.160 --> 01:16:00.490 align:middle line:84%
It was a cold, rainy
night in Zurich.

01:16:00.490 --> 01:16:02.950 align:middle line:84%
And Judy asked, would
I see if I could

01:16:02.950 --> 01:16:05.980 align:middle line:90%
bring forward Mary Magdalene.

01:16:05.980 --> 01:16:09.760 align:middle line:84%
And this power came through
that just throttled both of us.

01:16:09.760 --> 01:16:11.420 align:middle line:90%
It was so amazing.

01:16:11.420 --> 01:16:14.920 align:middle line:84%
I've worked with a lot of
beings of different traditions,

01:16:14.920 --> 01:16:17.580 align:middle line:90%
and this one was like, wow.

01:16:17.580 --> 01:16:20.825 align:middle line:84%
I don't know what this is, but
this is power and intelligence.

01:16:20.825 --> 01:16:35.680 align:middle line:90%


01:16:35.680 --> 01:16:39.034 align:middle line:90%
[CHANTING AND SINGING]

01:16:39.034 --> 01:18:03.460 align:middle line:90%


01:18:03.460 --> 01:18:06.630 align:middle line:10%
What Magdalen was
saying is, that the time

01:18:06.630 --> 01:18:10.780 align:middle line:10%
has come for the feminine
to be raised up in balance

01:18:10.780 --> 01:18:14.870 align:middle line:10%
to the male in a way differently
than has been done in the past.

01:18:14.870 --> 01:18:19.660 align:middle line:84%
Living in authenticity with
each other in relationship,

01:18:19.660 --> 01:18:22.910 align:middle line:84%
and speaking your truth no
matter how difficult, no matter

01:18:22.910 --> 01:18:26.050 align:middle line:90%
how embarrassing it is.

01:18:26.050 --> 01:18:28.355 align:middle line:84%
And out of that cauldron--
and it is a cauldron.

01:18:28.355 --> 01:18:31.720 align:middle line:84%
It's like a furnace, because
when you speak your truth,

01:18:31.720 --> 01:18:35.620 align:middle line:84%
things that are not
true get burned away.

01:18:35.620 --> 01:18:37.374 align:middle line:84%
And in that process,
both are elevated--

01:18:37.374 --> 01:18:38.362 align:middle line:90%
the male and the female.

01:18:38.362 --> 01:19:03.150 align:middle line:90%


01:19:03.150 --> 01:19:06.780 align:middle line:84%
I believe that we're
all on our own paths,

01:19:06.780 --> 01:19:10.850 align:middle line:84%
and the path of alchemy was
an internal one that you

01:19:10.850 --> 01:19:12.780 align:middle line:90%
did yourself, for yourself.

01:19:12.780 --> 01:19:15.794 align:middle line:84%
And Magdalen basically
took the blinders off,

01:19:15.794 --> 01:19:16.960 align:middle line:84%
and said, well,
there's another way

01:19:16.960 --> 01:19:19.760 align:middle line:84%
to look at this, which
is that you can engage

01:19:19.760 --> 01:19:23.750 align:middle line:90%
in relationship as a path.

01:19:23.750 --> 01:19:27.030 align:middle line:84%
And the alchemy can be shared
between two people that

01:19:27.030 --> 01:19:32.450 align:middle line:84%
are peers, and travel
together on this path

01:19:32.450 --> 01:19:34.090 align:middle line:84%
to greater understanding
and enlightenment.

01:19:34.090 --> 01:19:39.150 align:middle line:90%


01:19:39.150 --> 01:19:42.140 align:middle line:84%
But fundamentally, at a deeper
level, what her message is

01:19:42.140 --> 01:19:45.690 align:middle line:84%
about is an urgent
message, which

01:19:45.690 --> 01:19:49.570 align:middle line:84%
is that if we are to survive,
we must raise the feminine

01:19:49.570 --> 01:19:54.330 align:middle line:84%
out the ashes that we have
created as a global culture

01:19:54.330 --> 01:19:57.210 align:middle line:84%
for centuries, and have
the two meet together--

01:19:57.210 --> 01:20:01.480 align:middle line:84%
male and female together--
not one above the other,

01:20:01.480 --> 01:20:02.860 align:middle line:90%
but in equality.

01:20:02.860 --> 01:20:06.953 align:middle line:84%
And with that union,
create a new world.

01:20:06.953 --> 01:20:12.244 align:middle line:90%


01:20:12.244 --> 01:20:16.228 align:middle line:90%
[CHANTING AND SINGING]

01:20:16.228 --> 01:23:39.780 align:middle line:90%


01:23:39.780 --> 01:23:43.380 align:middle line:84%
I think the quest has
actually ended, as I

01:23:43.380 --> 01:23:47.240 align:middle line:90%
think about it in this moment.

01:23:47.240 --> 01:23:49.500 align:middle line:84%
So I feel that the
work between the human

01:23:49.500 --> 01:23:52.510 align:middle line:84%
and the spiritual
part of me has ended.

01:23:52.510 --> 01:23:54.750 align:middle line:90%
I've unified the two.

01:23:54.750 --> 01:23:57.550 align:middle line:90%
That war is done.

01:23:57.550 --> 01:24:01.740 align:middle line:84%
It's not that the
learning has ended,

01:24:01.740 --> 01:24:07.000 align:middle line:84%
but the tension between
the human and the spiritual

01:24:07.000 --> 01:24:07.700 align:middle line:90%
has ended.

01:24:07.700 --> 01:24:12.370 align:middle line:90%


01:24:12.370 --> 01:24:16.130 align:middle line:84%
And the final piece of that is
realizing that the boy who sang

01:24:16.130 --> 01:24:20.180 align:middle line:84%
to the world, he had
a misunderstanding,

01:24:20.180 --> 01:24:22.660 align:middle line:84%
and his misunderstanding
was that he could resolve

01:24:22.660 --> 01:24:24.470 align:middle line:90%
the suffering of others.

01:24:24.470 --> 01:24:28.310 align:middle line:84%
All he really needs
to do is be a witness,

01:24:28.310 --> 01:24:31.550 align:middle line:84%
because everyone is responsible
for their own happiness.

01:24:31.550 --> 01:24:34.460 align:middle line:84%
So as the boy who sang to
the world has grown up,

01:24:34.460 --> 01:24:37.230 align:middle line:84%
and he's no longer singing
the hopes and dreams of people

01:24:37.230 --> 01:24:41.490 align:middle line:84%
into existence, he's singing
a space that allows them

01:24:41.490 --> 01:24:42.955 align:middle line:90%
to create that for themselves.

